title: Paku
description:
Release Date: 12 Dec 2013

Language:Malay

Subtitle: -

Genre:Horror / Thriller

Running Time: 90 minutes

Director:P. Rameesh

Cast:Johan Asari, Aishah Ilias, Diana Johor, Azad Jasmin, Kamal Adli

Synopsis:
When Fahmi loses his wife Rania due to childbirth, he becomes desperate. Left to raise his eldest son alone, Fahmi decides that he has to bring his wife back to life so that his son would not have to grow up without a mother. After extensive research, Fahmi discovers that it is possible through the means of black magic - by hammering a nail into Rania's skull. But the woman that awakens is not the wife he once knew...
